	  RNTrack: A FTN Messages tracker
	  Version 1.13

     What is this program for
     ------------------------
     It is so called netmail "tracker". It's puprose is to process netmail on
netmail hubs, though it can be useful for an ordinary node. It parses PKTs or
messagebases, compare messages with patterns and doing specified action if
pattern matched. Also RNTrack may be used for echomail with limitations.

     Features
     --------
* Support for popular messagebases: OPUS (*.msg), JAM, Squish.
* Support for PKT 2+.
* Embedded Perl (if scripting is enabled at compile time).
* External templates.
* Portability.

     Documentation
     -------------
     The doc and samples subdirectory is contain documentation. Also you may
subscribe to RU.FTRACK Fidonet echoarea and visits project's web page
http://sourceforge.net/projects/rntrack.

     Bug reporting
     -------------
     Read BUG-REPORTING text file for details.

